                                                            <p style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp;</p>
                                                            <p style="color:rgba(49, 49, 49, 0.7);"><span style="font-family:Roboto;"><span style="color:rgb(53, 53, 53);">Alivecasino takes responsibility for the security of its players. Protection of the players is based on preventing under age players from participating in games and the protection of privacy, which involves responsible processing of personal data and payments. Fairness and the random nature of the products offered are monitored closely by independent organisations. Marketing communications are also created with player protection and fairness in mind.</span></span></p>
