                                                        <div class="uc-content ">
                                                            <h5 style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="color:rgb(53, 53, 53);"><strong>Protection of minors</strong></span></h5>
                                                            <p style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp;</p>
                                                            <p style="color:rgba(49, 49, 49, 0.7);"><span style="font-family:Roboto;"><span style="color:rgb(53, 53, 53);">Alivecasino does not allow minors (persons under the age of 18 or whatever the minimum age to gamble is within the customers jurisdiction of residence) to participate in games and place bets. For this reason, confirmation of age and date of birth are mandatory requirements during registration. Alivecasino takes the issue of minors taking part in games and betting very seriously. In order to offer the best possible protection of minors, Alivecasino also relies on the support of their parents and caregivers. Alivecasino advises its customers to keep their data for account access in a safe place (user ID and password) and to not disclose this data to anyone.</span></span></p>
                                                            <p style="color:rgba(49, 49, 49, 0.7);">&nbsp;</p>
                                                            <p style="color:rgba(49, 49, 49, 0.7);"><span style="font-family:Roboto;"><span style="color:rgb(53, 53, 53);">Furthermore, Alivecasino would recommend that customers install filter software. This software will allow customers to restrict the access to Internet resources inappropriate for children and teenagers.</span></span></p>
