                                                        <div class="uc-content ">
                                                            <h5 style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="color:rgb(53, 53, 53);"><strong>Responsibility towards problems</strong></span></h5>
                                                            <p style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp;</p>
                                                            <p style="color:rgba(49, 49, 49, 0.7);"><span style="font-family:Roboto;"><span style="color:rgb(53, 53, 53);">Alivecasino offers a variety of games and bets which are forms of entertainment for the majority of customers. At the same time, the company takes responsibility for its customers by providing support and tools for maintenance of a secure and entertaining environment, taking into account the associated risks.</span></span></p>
                                                            <p style="color:rgba(49, 49, 49, 0.7);">&nbsp;</p>
                                                            <p style="color:rgba(49, 49, 49, 0.7);"><span style="font-family:Roboto;"><span style="color:rgb(53, 53, 53);">Clients who have difficulty in assessing risks, recognizing their own limits or those who suffer from problem gambling are potentially not able to enjoy the product line-up responsibly and do not perceive it as a form of entertainment. Alivecasino may take responsibility for these users by blocking their access to certain products for their own protection.</span></span></p>
